{"text_id":235647,"tokens":["It"," is"," true"," that"," we"," should"," all"," strive"," to"," be"," more"," resilient"," in"," overcoming"," our"," issues",","," but"," denying"," the"," existence"," of"," triggers"," is"," ignoring"," a"," very"," real"," phenomenon","."," Triggers"," are"," cues"," in"," the"," environment"," which"," evoke"," strong"," emotional"," reactions"," related"," to"," past"," traumatic"," experiences","."," These"," reactions"," can"," be"," so"," intense"," that"," they"," can"," interfere"," with"," our"," day","-","to","-","day"," functioning"," and"," cause"," us"," to"," act"," out"," in"," ways"," that"," are"," not"," productive","."," Therefore",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," acknowledge"," that"," triggers"," exist",","," as"," understanding"," this"," can"," help"," us"," to"," better"," manage"," our"," emotions"," and"," reactions"," in"," response"," to"," them","."],"sub_source":"cmv","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}